#. <CLT 04>こうして２人でこの景色を見るのも<CLT>
#. <CLT 04>今日で最後か…<CLT>
msgctxt "0001"
msgid ""
"<CLT 4>I decided to talk to Hina one more time before we all\n"
"left...\n"
"<CLT>"
msgstr ""

#. <CLT 04>色々と無茶苦茶なサバイバル生活だったけど<CLT>
#. <CLT 04>改めて振り返ってみると…楽しかったな。<CLT>
msgctxt "0002"
msgid ""
"<CLT 4>I wonder if this is the last time we'll ever see this\n"
"place...\n"
"<CLT>"
msgstr ""

#. <CLT 04>なんだかんだ言っても、<CLT>
#. <CLT 04>人が死ぬような事態にはならなかったし。<CLT>
msgctxt "0003"
msgid ""
"<CLT 4>The time we spent here didn't make much sense,\n"
"but...looking back, I can't say I didn't have fun.\n"
"<CLT>"
msgstr ""

#. 修学旅行もこれでおしまいかぁ…
msgctxt "0004"
msgid ""
"<CLT 4>There are still some mysteries left. What was\n"
"Monokuma, really? Why'd we end up here?\n"
"<CLT>"
msgstr ""

#. みんな、元いた場所に帰っちゃうんだね。
msgctxt "0005"
msgid ""
"<CLT 4>I still don't have answers, but I'll have time to\n"
"figure all that out once we escape...\n"
"<CLT>"
msgstr ""

#. え…？
#. 何言ってんだ、お前もだろ？
msgctxt "0006"
msgid "Ahh...we can finally leave!"
msgstr ""

#. ん？
#. んー…そうだね。
msgctxt "0007"
msgid "Yeah, you're right."
msgstr ""

#. ねぇ、日向くん。
#. 日向くんはこの島に来て、良かった？
msgctxt "0008"
msgid ""
"But we never found out why this all happened in the\n"
"first place, huh?"
msgstr ""

#. ああ…今はそう思うよ。
msgctxt "0009"
msgid ""
"Someone tricked us, sure. But why would anyone wanna\n"
"do all of this!?"
msgstr ""

#. みんなと力を合わせて色々な事をして
#. 少しは成長できたような気がする。
msgctxt "0010"
msgid "Hmm... Oh well!"
msgstr ""

#. みんなで過ごしたこの島の事、
#. 俺は絶対に忘れないよ。
msgctxt "0011"
msgid ""
"All I care about now is getting outta here and\n"
"stuffing as many donuts in my face as I can handle!"
msgstr ""

#. そっか…よかった…
msgctxt "0012"
msgid ""
"Glazed donuts, jelly donuts, chocolate donuts, bear\n"
"claws, crullers, berliners, you name it!"
msgstr ""

#. あたしもね、すごく成長できたと思うんだ。
msgctxt "0013"
msgid ""
"*Sigh* I'm just gonna eat and eat and eat till I pass\n"
"right out!"
msgstr ""

#. 日向クンがね、
#. 色々教えてくれたから…
msgctxt "0014"
msgid "Haha. So that's what's got you the most excited, huh?"
msgstr ""

#. あ…でも、苦手分野は
#. 相変わらず苦手なままだけど…
msgctxt "0015"
msgid "Huh? Well, what else is there?"
msgstr ""

#. <CLT 04>七海の苦手分野って…ゲームの、だよな。<CLT>
msgctxt "0016"
msgid "Oh, well, don't you remember what you said?"
msgstr ""

#. <CLT 04>それって確か…<CLT>
msgctxt "0017"
msgid "...Wait, what did you say again?"
msgstr ""

#. 格闘ゲーム
msgctxt "0018"
msgid "...Wait, what did you say again?"
msgstr ""

#. 七海の苦手なのって…格闘ゲームだっけ？
msgctxt "0019"
msgid "Umm...I'm not sure why you're asking me."
msgstr ""

#. 得意ってほどではないけど
#. 日向くんにはたぶん負けないと思うよ。
msgctxt "0020"
msgid "R-Right. Umm..."
msgstr ""

#. <CLT 04>違ったみたいだな…<CLT>
msgctxt "0021"
msgid "Weren't you gonna go on a diet?"
msgstr ""

#. ハイスピード推理アクションゲーム
msgctxt "0022"
msgid "Weren't you gonna go on a diet?"
msgstr ""

#. ハイスピード推理アクションゲーム…
#. って、なかったっけ？
msgctxt "0023"
msgid ""
"I-I don't need to go on a diet! Cuz I'm not fat! I'm\n"
"not, right!?"
msgstr ""

#. それが苦手だったら、今頃生きてここに
#. いないような気がするんだよね。
msgctxt "0024"
msgid "A-Actually, yeah. You look the same as ever."
msgstr ""

#. <CLT 04>なぜか激しく同感だ…<CLT>
msgctxt "0025"
msgid ""
"<CLT 4>I need to say the right thing, before my momentum\n"
"takes a gut punch...\n"
"<CLT>"
msgstr ""

#. 恋愛ゲーム
msgctxt "0026"
msgid ""
"<CLT 4>So...\n"
"<CLT>"
msgstr ""

#. 恋愛ゲーム、だったよな。
#. 七海が苦手なのって。
msgctxt "0027"
msgid "Weren't you gonna go for the gold?"
msgstr ""

#. 前より興味は持てたから、
#. 色々勉強はしてみたんだけどね…
msgctxt "0028"
msgid "..."
msgstr "..."

#. ………………
msgctxt "0029"
msgid ""
"Weren't you gonna go for the gold? Even if it means\n"
"you're a \"super gold spaz\"?"
msgstr ""

#. ねぇ、日向くん…
#. わたしの事…どう思ってる？
msgctxt "0030"
msgid "Nng...! Why'd you have to bring up that last part!?"
msgstr ""

#. え…え！？
msgctxt "0031"
msgid "Ah, s-sorry! It's not like *I* see you that way!"
msgstr ""

#. きゅ、急に言われても…
msgctxt "0032"
msgid ""
"It's just...that's your goal, right? I thought you\n"
"wanted to do whatever it took to reach it."
msgstr ""

#. ええと、俺は…七海の事――
msgctxt "0033"
msgid ""
"Well yeah, of course that's my goal! I'm gonna keep on\n"
"aiming higher and higher!"
msgstr ""

#. あ、やっぱダメ。
msgctxt "0034"
msgid "B-But..."
msgstr ""

#. …はい？
msgctxt "0035"
msgid ""
"I just thought that the very first thing I wanted to\n"
"do when we got out was go get a donut with you..."
msgstr ""

#. よく考えたら、何か言われても
#. どう対応すればいいかよくわからないや。
msgctxt "0036"
msgid ""
"With me...? But I mean...we're together right now,\n"
"right?"
msgstr ""

#. やっぱり難しいなぁ…
msgctxt "0037"
msgid "No, it's no good here! Cuz, I mean..."
msgstr ""

#. <CLT 04>ホッとしたような残念なような…<CLT>
msgctxt "0038"
msgid ""
"This isn't a good place to do another practice run!\n"
"I wanna do more date testing!"
msgstr ""

#. <CLT 04>複雑な心境だ…<CLT>
msgctxt "0039"
msgid "More date testing...? You still wanna keep doing that?"
msgstr ""

#. えっとね、次までにもうちょっと勉強しとく。
#. だから………
msgctxt "0040"
msgid ""
"I remember what you said before. That it's okay for me\n"
"to be me."
msgstr ""

#. これからもわたしに…色々教えてくれる？
msgctxt "0041"
msgid "And I understand that."
msgstr ""

#. …あたりまえだろ。
msgctxt "0042"
msgid ""
"Who I am right now is the best me there is! And a\n"
"second later, THAT'S the best me there is!"
msgstr ""

#. 七海が知りたいこと、
#. 俺がなんだって教えてやるよ。
msgctxt "0043"
msgid ""
"Okay, so...why do you want to keep doing these\n"
"\"practice runs\"?"
msgstr ""

#. …って、俺が知ってることなんて
#. そんなにあるわけじゃないけど。
msgctxt "0044"
msgid "W-Well...how about if it's *not* a practice run?"
msgstr ""

#. そんなのいいの！
#. わたしは日向くんに教わりたいんだから。
msgctxt "0045"
msgid "Would you go on...a r-real date with me?"
msgstr ""

#. っていうかね、その…
msgctxt "0046"
msgid "...Yeah, that sounds nice."
msgstr ""

#. 日向くんじゃなきゃ…嫌だから…
msgctxt "0047"
msgid "R-Really!? You really want to!?"
msgstr ""

#. …わかったよ。
#. 俺も次までに色々勉強しとくから。
msgctxt "0048"
msgid ""
"Even if I'm all CHOMP CHOMP GULP CHOMP on donuts all\n"
"the time, you won't get grossed out?"
msgstr ""

#. うん…約束だよ？
msgctxt "0049"
msgid "That's just who you are, right?"
msgstr ""

#. わたし、待ってる。
msgctxt "0050"
msgid ""
"If I said it was gross, and you had to try to change\n"
"to make me happy, that wouldn't be any fun."
msgstr ""

#. …待ってるからね。
msgctxt "0051"
msgid ""
"Y-Yeah, you're right! True love is when two people can\n"
"be themselves and still have fun with each other!"
msgstr ""

#. <CLT 04>…しっかりと手を繋ぐ。<CLT>
msgctxt "0052"
msgid "And I like who you are right now, too!"
msgstr ""

#. <CLT 04>手を離したら、七海が消えてしまいそうな<CLT>
#. <CLT 04>気がして…怖かった。<CLT>
msgctxt "0053"
msgid ""
"...Ah, crap! I was gonna wait and say all that stuff\n"
"on our date."
msgstr ""

#. <CLT 04>それでも、例え何が起ころうと、<CLT>
#. <CLT 04>七海との約束だけは必ず守ってみせる。<CLT>
msgctxt "0054"
msgid "B-But that's just me too, right? The blunt me..."
msgstr ""

#. <CLT 04>繋いだこの手こそがきっと、<CLT>
#. <CLT 04>俺にとっての"希望"の象徴だから…<CLT>
msgctxt "0055"
msgid ""
"Without you, I'd never have the confidence to just be\n"
"myself. Thank you..."
msgstr ""

#. はい
msgctxt "0056"
msgid ""
"So now you're gonna be by my side like, all the time,\n"
"right? No, more than that! Together forever!"
msgstr ""

#. いいえ
msgctxt "0057"
msgid ""
"<CLT 4>Hina's smile when she said that was positively\n"
"dazzling.\n"
"<CLT>"
msgstr ""

#. <CLT 06>他にも話しかけたい人がいますか？<CLT>
msgctxt "0058"
msgid ""
"<CLT 4>No matter how dark things might get for me, as long as\n"
"I have that smile by my side, I'll be okay.\n"
"<CLT>"
msgstr ""

#. <CLT 04>こうして俺たちの<CLT>
#. <CLT 04>南の島での生活は終わりを告げた――<CLT>
msgctxt "0059"
msgid ""
"<CLT 4>To me, Hina is the embodiment of that ray of hope...\n"
"<CLT>"
msgstr ""

